en.title: Taiwan's expulsion of mainland wives has attracted global attention!
en.description:
How will the United States deal with Yaya as it keeps a close eye on Taiwan? The whole world is watching the expulsion of the mainland spouses from the armed reunification... Special report from foreign media special correspondents stationed in Taiwan!
The remarks about military reunification have crossed the red line of the first island chain! Yaya scolded Taiwan: It will become a ruin in half an hour! Otherwise, why would we build so many aircraft carriers!
Two major French newspapers come to Taiwan to investigate the "CCP's spy war against Taiwan"! Exclusive interview with Taiwanâ€™s Inspector Generalâ€¦exposing that communist spies are hiding â€œamong Taiwanese citizensâ€!
Taiwan has been infiltrated and is in a mess... Can't the allies stand it anymore? Europe and the United States have successively called on Taiwan to "increase penalties for espionage"!
Foreign media revealed that China can "blockade Taiwan today" and Taiwan and the United States have already made up their mind! ? The US immediately released photos of "US troops in Taiwan"! ?
Is the US dissatisfied with Taiwanâ€™s reliance on imports for 96% of its energy? Construction of a 1,300km submarine natural gas pipeline "Alaska via Japan" directly to Taiwan! ?
The number of times US bombers fly close to Taiwan has doubled! ? The US military comes 343 days out of 365 days a year... Chinese think tanks are so scared that they are writing a report urgently! ?
Itâ€™s not just Taiwan thatâ€™s arresting â€œcommunist spy internet celebritiesâ€! Philippine officials admit that "China feeds internet celebrities" to spread false pro-China information on South China Sea sovereignty!
The US-Philippines military exercise was watched in full! ? The "province closest to Taiwan" was secretly photographed by spies... There are 4,600 Chinese students in local schools! ?
The Philippine female mayor and the Chinese spy have "exactly the same fingerprints"! ? The head of KK Park testified that he "had cooperated with her to infiltrate"!
New York Governor's Assistant is a "Chinese Communist Party Female Spy"! ? To help expand influence... China rewards US$15.76 million and luxury homes and cars!
China is ruthless in spending money on spies! Sun Wen has infiltrated the US government for 14 years...traveling around the political circle and taking photos to "make 500 million"!
Before leaving the country, Chinese partner Yaya shouted "I'm leaving with a clean bill of health" and refused to admit her mistake! Wang: The court "showed its strength" by quickly dismissing the appeal!
Yaya was expelled...the Kuomintang jumped out to support her and "added fuel to the fire"? Wang: There are still 71 "pro-China internet celebrities" reported and awaiting investigation!
Chinese internet celebrity scolded Yaya, "Get out if you need to," and called on the Immigration Bureau to not be lenient! Huang: Donâ€™t drag down the other 300,000 RMB!

snippet.description:
Learn how to turn a cactus into a water flask in the desert! In this desert survival hack, we'll show you a game-changing technique to extract water from a cactus and create a makeshift water bottle to quench your thirst in the arid wilderness. From finding the right type of cactus to harvesting the water, we'll take you through every step of this innovative survival skill. Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast, a desert explorer, or just someone who wants to be prepared for any situation, this desert survival hack is a must-know technique that could save your life. So, watch until the end to learn how to create a cactus water flask and stay hydrated in the desert!
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brave.gals

In this desert survival hack, we'll show you a game-changing technique to extract water from a cactus and create a makeshift water bottle to quench your thirst in the arid wilderness. From finding the right type of cactus to harvesting the water, we'll take you through every step of this innovative survival skill. Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast, a desert explorer, or just someone who wants to be prepared for any situation, this desert survival hack is a must-know technique that could save your life. So, watch until the end to learn how to create a cactus water flask and stay hydrated in the desert!
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brave.gals

#tourism #hack #diy #skills #survival #outdoors #camping
tourism hack diy skills survival outdoors camping
